*劉改女，女，77歲；有三成皮膚被火燒傷，送院後證實死亡<ref name="mingpao_gaa1h">{{cite news|url=http://www.mingpaonews.com/20080811/gaa1h.htm|title=旺角災難五級火 氧氣分市民 兩消防殉職|publisher=明報|date=2008-08-11|accessdate=2008-08-11|archive-date=2008-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081027100118/http://www.mingpaonews.com/20080811/gaa1h.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>
